creator: Vedaist
descriptionHtml:
Vedaist is a beautiful and intuitive English dictionary. Search the massive dictionary catalog with over 800,000 words. Vedaist is a must-have tool for avid readers, new learners or just about anyone looking to level up their vocabulary. The app is designed so that you will have loads of fun along the way.

Our dictionary is powered by Wikipedia sites for up-to-date meanings. Words and meanings are cross referenced for better context. Related words like similar, opposites and also broad or narrower definitions are included. Thousands of images are present for visual learning. Browsing words has never been as exciting.

Get a new curated Word of the day for a challenge.

Set a personal monthly goal and track progress. Get fun prizes if you meet your goals!

Save and bookmark your favorite words. Revisit words that matter to you.

We do not have advertisement trackers. We are proud of our clean design without any clutter for an uninterrupted learning experience.

Happy exploring!
descriptionShort: Ad free beautiful modern dictionary with meanings, daily words, images and more.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We've added related words (thesaurus entries) in this release. For select words you can see similar, opposites and also broad or narrower definitions.
